_json.gridTitle: Father Refuses to Allow 6-Year-Old Son to Dress Like a Girl – Now He's Been Charged with 'Child Abuse'
_json.description: URGENT PRAYER REQUEST - Father Refuses to Allow 6yr old Son to Dress like a Girl – Now he’s been Falsely Charged with ‘Child Abuse’: A Texas father is in the middle of a high stakes legal battle that could end in him losing his son. Jeffrey Younger will not affirm his ex-wife's decision to raise their 6yr old son James Younger as a girl. The mother, who calls their son ‘Luna’ wants to force the father to pay for transgender therapy and hormone therapy for their son when he turns 8.
